me":"text-white/70","children":"A platform that generates 100 leads at $10 each with 1% conversion is worse than one that generates 20 leads at $40 each with 10% conversion."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":2}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Online leads require fast response",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"AI response tools like Structurely are not optional when buying online leads — the 5-minute response window is real data, and human follow-up usually can't match it."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":3}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Sphere vs. online",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"Your sphere and past clients convert at 10-15x the rate of online leads. Before investing in lead generation technology, ensure you have a system for your sphere."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":4}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Geographic competition",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"Lead quality varies significantly by market. Get references from agents in your specific market before committing to a lead generation platform."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":5}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Six-month minimum commitment",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"Lead generation ROI is measured over 6-12 months. Any platform that requires month-to-month commitments is either very confident or trying to trap you — verify which."}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"Frequently Asked Questions"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","details","0",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Which AI lead generation platform has the best ROI for real estate?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Based on agent-reported data, organic/SEO-driven leads from platforms like Sierra Interactive have the best ROI (CAC $500-1,500/transaction). Paid social and Zillow Premier Agent leads range $1,500-3,000+/transaction. Predictive prospecting (Likely.ai) has variable ROI that improves significantly with a consistent outreach system behind it."}]]}],["$","details","1",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Is buying Zillow Premier Agent worth it?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"At 2026 prices, Zillow Premier Agent pencils for agents who have strong conversion rates (3%+ of leads to transactions) and excellent follow-up systems. At average conversion rates (1-2%), it's marginal to negative ROI in most markets. The key is having both the lead follow-up infrastructure (Structurely or similar) and the CRM discipline to work leads for 12-18 months."}]]}],["$","details","2",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["What's the difference between lead generation and lead qualification?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Lead generation creates new contacts who've expressed interest in real estate. Lead qualification filters those contacts to identify who's actually ready to transact and who has the motivation, timeline, and financial capability to close. The best ROI comes from combining quality lead generation with aggressive AI qualification — not just generating more raw leads."}]]}],["$","details","3",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["How do AI tools improve Facebook and Google real estate ads?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"AI tools improve ad performance through automated audience optimization, dynamic creative testing, and smart budget allocation across campaigns. Platforms like Lofty and Sierra Interactive have built-in ad management that uses AI to optimize targeting. Third-party tools like Adwerx focus specifically on automated real estate advertising."}]]}],["$","details","4",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Is predictive analytics (Likely.ai) better than buying leads?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Over a 12-18 month horizon, predictive prospecting typically produces higher-quality leads at lower cost than buying online leads. The difference is timing: buying leads produces activity now; predictive prospecting builds pipeline for 6-18 months from now. The best strategy combines both — buy leads for immediate activity, build predictive prospecting for future pipeline."}]]}],["$","details","5",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["How many leads do I need per month to justify AI tools?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Follow Up Boss: 10+ leads/month. Lofty: 30+ leads/month. Structurely: 50+ leads/month (where 24/7 response becomes critical). Likely.ai: Based on farm size, typically worth it with a 200+ home farm. At lower volumes, personal follow-up is more cost-effective."}]]}],["$","details","6",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Can I generate leads with AI without spending money on advertising?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bo